This is a colorful,
fun, auto-runner game,

00:26:48.466 --> 00:26:50.036 A:middle
and you may be familiar with it,

00:26:50.396 --> 00:26:52.316 A:middle
because it is an ADA
winner this year.

00:26:53.016 --> 00:26:54.376 A:middle
But, that's not why
I'm including it.

00:26:54.546 --> 00:26:56.896 A:middle
I have it here for a
completely different reason.

00:26:58.006 --> 00:27:00.796 A:middle
So, let's just say that I
downloaded Chameleon Run


WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:26:58.006 --> 00:27:00.796 A:middle
So, let's just say that I
downloaded Chameleon Run

00:27:00.796 --> 00:27:04.106 A:middle
from the app store, and I've
never launched this game before.

00:27:05.516 --> 00:27:08.936 A:middle
So, let's just see what
happens when I click open.

00:27:21.476 --> 00:27:22.536 A:middle
Did you guys see that?

00:27:23.266 --> 00:27:24.486 A:middle
It was awesome.

00:27:24.866 --> 00:27:26.946 A:middle
We were instantly into the game.

00:27:27.016 --> 00:27:28.266 A:middle
We just started playing.

00:27:28.896 --> 00:27:31.876 A:middle
Right from launch you're in
and you're playing the game.

00:27:32.076 --> 00:27:33.576 A:middle
And that is awesome.

00:27:34.416 --> 00:27:36.776 A:middle
So, now I just want to continue

00:27:36.776 --> 00:27:38.346 A:middle
through this first
level a little bit more,

00:27:39.056 --> 00:27:42.306 A:middle
because there's something
else special that is going on.

00:27:42.876 --> 00:27:47.166 A:middle
You are reading a text,
and seeing the animation

00:27:47.166 --> 00:27:49.466 A:middle
on the Siri Remote, and
watching your runner,

00:27:50.036 --> 00:27:51.346 A:middle
all at the same time.

00:27:52.506 --> 00:27:54.186 A:middle
The texting graphics are clear.

00:27:54.186 --> 00:27:57.846 A:middle
So, you're able to play and
learn at the exact same time.

00:27:58.426 --> 00:27:59.836 A:middle
And that is fantastic.


