So, when you pass
this first level,

00:28:10.526 --> 00:28:14.316 A:middle
which is your first experience
in the game, you get this party.

00:28:14.316 --> 00:28:15.516 A:middle
And you feel great.

00:28:15.996 --> 00:28:17.106 A:middle
You feel accomplished.

00:28:17.576 --> 00:28:20.296 A:middle
And now you're just
welcomed to play more.

00:28:21.656 --> 00:28:24.356 A:middle
Chameleon Run is so much
fun on the Siri Remote.

00:28:24.756 --> 00:28:26.236 A:middle
It has great game play.

00:28:26.626 --> 00:28:28.376 A:middle
And they support
game controllers too.

00:28:29.196 --> 00:28:32.326 A:middle
But, most of all I love
that you're immediately able

00:28:32.326 --> 00:28:35.246 A:middle
to jump into the game.

00:28:35.446 --> 00:28:38.316 A:middle
Now, granted not every single
app or game can do this.

00:28:38.756 --> 00:28:41.716 A:middle
But, you should still
consider what you need to do

00:28:41.716 --> 00:28:45.046 A:middle
to make your apps experience
easy, and as quick to jump

00:28:45.096 --> 00:28:48.836 A:middle
to as possible, because
that's why people are there.

00:28:49.006 --> 00:28:50.906 A:middle
They just want to
jump into your app.

00:28:51.496 --> 00:28:53.016 A:middle
And that's Chameleon Run.

