00:28:58.616 --> 00:29:00.476 A:middle
And it is called, Late Shift.

00:29:02.156 --> 00:29:03.926 A:middle
This is a cinematic game

00:29:04.236 --> 00:29:06.256 A:middle
that lets you control
the main character.

00:29:07.276 --> 00:29:10.506 A:middle
Decisions you make change
what happens in the movie.

00:29:11.146 --> 00:29:13.276 A:middle
And if you want to watch
and play with friends,

00:29:13.606 --> 00:29:16.016 A:middle
there's a companion app for the
iPhone that you can download

00:29:16.016 --> 00:29:17.296 A:middle
and make decisions together.

00:29:18.766 --> 00:29:21.596 A:middle
So, potentially you
could have a protagonist

00:29:21.596 --> 00:29:23.256 A:middle
that then turns into
an antagonist.

00:29:23.766 --> 00:29:26.756 A:middle
This is a
choose-your-own-adventure game

00:29:26.786 --> 00:29:30.806 A:middle
with a really easy
navigation, navigational bottle

00:29:31.216 --> 00:29:33.096 A:middle
and a very simple
level selection UI.

00:29:33.216 --> 00:29:37.506 A:middle
And the majority of your
experience is inside this film.

00:29:38.126 --> 00:29:40.836 A:middle
And this game play is
great on the big screen.

00:29:41.316 --> 00:29:43.816 A:middle
You control the movie's
plot from your Siri Remote.

00:29:44.936 --> 00:29:46.316 A:middle
The onboarding is integrated

00:29:46.316 --> 00:29:47.826 A:middle
into the first level's
voice over.

00:29:48.126 --> 00:29:50.456 A:middle
And it lets you know
the important of choice.

00:29:51.716 --> 00:29:54.436 A:middle
Late Shift is an intriguing,
entertainment hybrid

00:29:54.686 --> 00:29:57.386 A:middle
that I'm really excited
to see emerging

00:29:57.386 --> 00:29:58.856 A:middle
in apps on the Apple TV.


